121
00:16:37,383 --> 00:16:40,093
Yes, I'm getting dressed.

122
00:16:47,983 --> 00:16:51,313
I don't want to.

123
00:16:53,653 --> 00:16:55,533
Come close to your mother.

124
00:17:07,253 --> 00:17:08,413
Smile!

125
00:17:26,043 --> 00:17:28,123
You must really look down on me!

126
00:17:29,903 --> 00:17:30,993
Why?

127
00:17:33,673 --> 00:17:37,763
Because I didn't do anything...

128
00:17:42,433 --> 00:17:44,333
You're still thinking about that rabbit?

129
00:17:45,373 --> 00:17:51,983
Yeah. Whenever I took the rabbit in my arms,
he would kick on my breasts with his legs.

130
00:17:54,053 --> 00:17:56,773
- Your breasts?
- Yeah, right here.

131
00:17:57,793 --> 00:17:59,223
Right here.

132
00:18:01,653 --> 00:18:05,423
You look so happy whenever
you talk about the rabbit.

133
00:18:10,453 --> 00:18:15,113
Should we go out to eat?
I've got a bit of money today.

134
00:18:20,103 --> 00:18:21,703
How about a Western restaurant?

135
00:18:23,513 --> 00:18:25,293
I don't know how to eat there.

136
00:18:25,663 --> 00:18:28,063
No problem, I'll teach you.

137
00:18:29,323 --> 00:18:35,063
There are certain things in this world,
which I left inside a cave.

138
00:18:35,883 --> 00:18:38,473
I slept wherever I could find a bed.

139
00:18:40,443 --> 00:18:42,443
And while soundly sleeping, I dreamed.

140
00:18:43,523 --> 00:18:45,303
In a dream, I saw a man
with a wooden stick.

141
00:18:46,233 --> 00:18:50,363
He came out of a dark room.
In his other hand, he was holding a book.

142
00:18:51,833 --> 00:18:57,663
His back was bent under the weight
of his luggage, just standing there.

143
00:19:00,073 --> 00:19:01,363
I was looking at him!

144
00:19:02,343 --> 00:19:04,963
