163
00:21:12,553 --> 00:21:16,683
Well, I think I'll bring you here
for your next birthday.

164
00:21:27,813 --> 00:21:29,483
Do you know these people?

165
00:21:29,673 --> 00:21:31,203
Can we sit here?

166
00:21:38,903 --> 00:21:41,083
- Your girlfriend?
- No, my sister.

167
00:21:41,363 --> 00:21:44,113
- Let me introduce you. This is Reiko.
- How do you do?

168
00:21:44,483 --> 00:21:45,813
